Titolo: Bad Street Brawler

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: Bad Street Brawler, originally released for home computers as Bop'n Rumble in North America and as Street Hassle in Europe, is a 1987 video game by Beam Software. Versions were released for the ZX Spectrum and Commodore 64 and MS-DOS by Melbourne House and Mindscape with a NES version following in 1989. The NES version was one of only two NES games specifically designed for use with Mattel's Power Glove.

Genere: Beat \'em up

Valutazione: N/A
